2004-04-04 21:33  Reuben Thomas  <rrt@sc3d.org>

	* NEWS, TODO, doc/zile.texi, src/Makefile.am, src/extern.h,
	  src/file.c, src/fontlock.c, src/funcs.c, src/line.c,
